ftp-client>help

=------------------- Command List         ----------------------=
|                                                                 |
| help            : Display All Command for the Client            |
|                                                                 |
| quit            : Quit The Sever                                |
|                                                                 |
| ls              : Display All file On the Ftp Server            |
|                                                                 |
| get <file>      : Download FIle from the Ftp Server             |
|                                                                 |
| put <file>      : Upload FIle to the Ftp Server                 |
| lpwd            :Display the current path                       |
| lcd <file>      : Open the file                                 |
| lrmdir <file>   : Delete the file On the Ftp Client             |
| lmkdir <file>   : Create the file On the Ftp Client             |
| rmdir <file>    : Delete the file On the Ftp Server             |
| mkdir <file>    : Create the file On the Ftp Server             |
| mput <file> ... :   Download FIles from the Ftp Server          |
| mget <file> ... :   Upload FIles from the Ftp Server            |
|                                                                 |
=-----------------------------------------------------------------=
